---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about SecureAutomation and our mission to help businesses automate securely.">
  <div class="container" style="padding: 4rem 0; max-width: 800px;">
    <h1>About SecureAutomation</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 2rem 0;">
      We help businesses leverage AI automation without compromising security.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Too many companies rush into automation tools without considering the security implications.
      We bridge that gap by reviewing, testing, and recommending tools that deliver both power and protection.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <ul style="line-height: 2;">
      <li>✅ In-depth tool reviews (AI automation, cybersecurity)</li>
      <li>✅ Head-to-head comparisons</li>
      <li>✅ Security-first implementation guides</li>
      <li>✅ No-fluff, data-driven recommendations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Transparency</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on this site are affiliate links. That means we may earn a commission if you purchase
      through our links (at no extra cost to you). We only recommend tools we've personally tested or
      thoroughly researched. Read our full <a href="/disclosure">affiliate disclosure</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
</style>
